I use "removeStorageItem(e.target.parentElement.children[0].textContent)" bcs i put the li and button in a div
i put the li and button in a div bcs the button have text and if you want to use "e.target.parentElement.textContent" then you get the text from li and button then you can't use the same code to delet the li from localstorage "itemStored = itemStored.filter(i => i !== item)"
if you use a icon in button then you can remove the div and use "e.target.parentElement.textContent"